channel.title: MY topic locked for NO reason?!?
channel.description: Hey guys, I put up my topic in the downloads section including my new harmscape source for everyone to download! Now its been locked for no exact reason! I was posting something to a guy called kill bill because he asked me about MY server source(harmscape) and didnt know how to start it. Now whats wrong about doing that in my thread which I made? I think i earn some respect for what I made public... Of course there i better sources, but to lock someones hard work for a reason that I cant understand? Maybe someone (including you mod tharaok!!!) could explain me this!! THanks!
